text: New York New Year 2026 Celebrations LIVE: Thousands Gather to Watch New York's Ball Drop & FireworksCrowds gather in Times Square to witness the iconic New Year’s Eve ball drop in New York City. Fireworks and confetti welcome 2026 as the ball rises again in red, white, and blue, marking the start of nationwide celebrations ahead of the United States’ upcoming 250th birthday.
